{"tid":394170,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯］而家諗返其實《屍速列車》啲喪屍好易解決","createTime":"2017-09-09T17:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T17:23:20.000Z","uid":27837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42793270303c43a153f47987047e3e5e930e2107","tid":394170,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"屁速列車入面啲喪屍甚至比the walking dead入面啲喪屍更易解決<br />\n<br />\n首先列車入面啲喪屍係冇嗅覺嘅<br />\n點解？因為有一幕佢哋入咗隧道之後啲喪屍就冇晒反應<br />\n眼前一黑乜都睇唔到，直至佢哋聽到有棒球跌落地先撲過去。<br />\n所以可以證明佢哋只有視覺和聽覺。<br />\n<br />\n咁好簡單，只要你哋三五成群一齊扮佢哋喺度亂咁fing，如果你扮唔到佢哋把聲甚至可以用錄音機錄低，之後放喺身上播。成件事解決。<br />\n主角三人組戇鳩鳩喺度同佢哋正面打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5506ec6e4639fe34046b55370ea8a76db26a6e","tid":394170,"uid":119158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:21:33.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，見到你都驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783d843a4026634d5402e2cac9e3f99cb1d37cf0","tid":394170,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦，見到你都驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思即係理論上係行得通<br />\n實質上就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}